{"id":61198,"type":1,"name":"銀のスプーン","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/aa/a5/61198_bc30s.jpg","summary":"　　自從父親過世後。今年就讀高三的律就與國一的弟弟‧調、小六的妹妹‧奏以及母親相依為命。\r\n　　某天母親因身體不適到醫院就醫，原以為只是咳嗽的小毛病，沒想到竟然需要住院長期治療，身為長男的律只好兄代母職，照料起弟妹的三餐及生活起居。\r\n　　在這之前從未站在廚房料理台前的律，雖然一開始有點不知所措，但看到弟妹吃了自己的料理後，臉上露出的那種滿足笑容，讓律因此愛上了作料理！","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>银色汤匙</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/9073\">小沢真理</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/128\">講談社</a>、<a href=\"/person/7033\">東立出版社</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/9072\">Kiss</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>銀色湯匙</li><li><span>开始: </span>2010年第15号</li>","collection":{"wish":2,"collect":1,"doing":1},"tags":[{"name":"漫画系列","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":9073,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/8d/49/9073_prsn_4UWwx.jpg","name":"小泽真理","desc":"作者"},{"id":128,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2f/b1/128_prsn_nHh14.jpg","name":"讲谈社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":7033,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/fd/24/7033_prsn_J3N83.jpg","name":"东立出版社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":9072,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/7f/4c/9072_prsn_Emf9r.jpg","name":"Kiss","desc":"连载杂志"}],"relations":[{"id":135615,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/d3/c3/135615_W8aAy.jpg","title":"明日もきっと、おいしいご飯～銀のスプーン～","type":"三次元","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/135615"}],"comic":[{"id":61192,"name":"銀のスプーン (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/f0/88/61192_jp.jpg"},{"id":61193,"name":"銀のスプーン (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/4b/a9/61193_jp.jpg"},{"id":61194,"name":"銀のスプーン (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/4a/95/61194_jp.jpg"},{"id":61195,"name":"銀のスプーン (4)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/93/f8/61195_jp.jpg"},{"id":61196,"name":"銀のスプーン (5)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/02/43/61196_jp.jpg"},{"id":61197,"name":"銀のスプーン (6)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/ba/f2/61197_jp.jpg"},{"id":75742,"name":"銀のスプーン (7)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/78/8f/75742_jp.jpg"},{"id":90395,"name":"銀のスプーン (8)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/20/23/90395_jp.jpg"},{"id":101804,"n